  "texts": [
    "One Extension: ATLA-K.",
    "The above ATLA optimization uses a single (Q, R) to learn adversarial X.",
    "We can easily extend it to ATLA-K, learning an adversarial trigger on a set of {(Q, R) k } K k=1.",
    "The search for X is supervised by the average of K losses.",
    "More details in App."
  ],
